遊行，呼籲教育界及家長帶同小朋友一齊參加！<br />\n<br />\n遊行已獲不反對通知書， 希望各位教育界人士，家長帶埋小朋友一同進場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行日期：23/11(星期六)<br />\n遊行時間：10:00a.m.<br />\n遊行地點：九龍塘沙福道》喇沙小學<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情請入Tg link : <a href=\"https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStopKillingOurKids&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8wg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=aef17f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cju0269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCju0269.jpg&h=63e6c479&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rd7aFTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frd7aFTR.jpg&h=ca0776ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twsU7yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwsU7yT.jpg&h=3c84c1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY2en7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY2en7e.jpg&h=8a342c95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFArYFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFArYFz.jpg&h=60fb1aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4o9b0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4o9b0A.jpg&h=8e8a1485&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnHU7yW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnHU7yW.jpg&h=e75d6ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登原post :<br />\n(家長x小朋友x教育工作者)23/11 保護小朋友遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744011</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3214a8bea2bf735b6e8b2ed34a72a7af96a94f00","tid":1744012,"uid":90269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"黎明行動"}]}